---
title: Quick Spiced Chicken Breast and Pepper Bulgur with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Yoghurt
description: It takes less than 25 minutes to make these Quick Spiced Chicken Breast and Pepper Bulgur. The spice here comes from chermoula and harissa, evoking the flavours of North African cuisine.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220404_R16_W20_UK_QR3538-16_MB_Main_low-81d3d79e.jpg
